  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of ADDERALL XR in the Treatment of Adolescents Aged 13-17 With Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Randomized, Multicenter, Double-blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-Controlled Safety and Efficacy Study of ADDERALL XR With an Open Label Extension, in the Treatment of Adolescents Aged 13-17 With ADHD</official_title>
  <sponsors>
